README:
This dataset contains data from 19 subjects on the theory of mind (ToM) localizer task ( (Saxe & Kanwisher, 2003).

This data was used to localize the right temporoparietal junction (RTPJ) in all subjects for a TMS experiment (Experiment 2 of Gaesser, B., Hirschfeld-Kroen, J., Horn, M., Wasserman, E. & Young, L. (under review)).
